### Initialize the game
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Response will contain:
### - game_id to use in subsequent requests
### - intro_narrative: AI-generated dynamic introduction to the game
### - message: Confirmation of game initialization
### 
### Example response:
### {
###   "game_id": 1,
###   "intro_narrative": "The cave entrance looms before you, a gaping maw in the mountainside...",
###   "message": "Game initialized with ID: 1"
### }